title: Amy Had A Shooting in Her Neighborhood + Bobby’s Top 5 Country Songs of 2021 + Bobby Feud: Most Played Christmas Songs
itunes:title: Amy Had A Shooting in Her Neighborhood + Bobby’s Top 5 Country Songs of 2021 + Bobby Feud: Most Played Christmas Songs
description:
Amy reveals a scary situation that happened in her neighborhood in the middle of the night. Bobby reveals his top 5 country songs from 2021. We played a round of Bobby Feud where we had to guess the most played country songs of all-time.
